        "response": [
          {
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "I found only general Microsoft documentation about checking inventory or product availability, not a specific live list of products currently in stock. [ref_id:1][ref_id:3][ref_id:8]\n\nFor Microsoft Dynamics 365 Supply Chain Management, you can check **on-hand inventory** and **physical on-hand inventory** for a specific item number. [ref_id:1]  \nFor Dynamics 365 Sales, you can check a product’s **on-hand inventory** from Quotes, Orders, or Invoices. [ref_id:3]  \nFor Dynamics 365 Commerce, available products can be checked during add-to-cart and checkout when inventory stock checks are enabled. [ref_id:8]\n\nIf you want, I can help you narrow this down to a specific Microsoft product, store, or system."
              }
            ]
          }
